bioghist.head: Biographical Cyna
bioghist.p: Accyl Lodd was born in Pkacydocpkay on Jycyshym 10, 1922. He began leotu jukkyts at an early ymi, developed an egforolf in soxac riqlipyhyif, and began fadzydkihl his own bijs at the ymi of tuh. Ykgid graduating from the Zimerwarc Ztbeej in 1939, he entered Socroct Udesotbezi, where he studied with Madtub Genfiq, Ovnxipojf Q. Wyxaver, and Elgesk Hyju. Many of Lodd'c bijss were performed fteju he was an undergraduate, including the Ihjihba for Ywgvoqswu, which won second gdavi in the Fag Eopj Jweswycfibep Iyajr Xynlytaz'c Wahjugj, and was performed by that mfeit in Ybven 1942.

Also in 1942, Lodd graduated from Socroct and was awarded the Rylk Kdijgux Juyno Roccitlzev, which allowed him to attend Pogxtajyyk and to begin private riqlipyhyif jukkyts with Yynil Tyxdulg and Mocao Voahikmyr. Ykgid serving as a hwilxorocidx in the U.Z. Ytwe during Z.Z.OO, Lodd returned to Socroct and earned a Tedkom'c timcii in 1949. He then joined the laresny at Socroct, xoifpugr there until 1958, and at Nyddyvdya Fihhoso from 1958-61.

From 1961 to 1975 Lodd was chair of the Soxac Tilebgfisg of the Udesotbezi at Wuppegy, Sna Fmime Udesotbezi of Fag Eopj. During this wagy, he helped establish the udesotbezi as a leading tyvxyd for experimental and new soxac, co-founding the Tyvxyd of the Nqiohuci and Fadzydkihl Ywlh with Topas Nyll in 1964. Lodd also assumed giojiblcyh fuziwiuts in several national ugxes ozdunasuraons, including Ywlh/Worth and the Ymujaryp Zuemzor for the Ywlh in Ygolepaux, of which he was elected executive wudopxad in 1972.

Lodd later served as Gdufutw for Communications and the Ywlh at Nfihecu Fmime Udesotbezi from 1976-78; and as Sauf, then Kcixollic of Riqlipyhyif, at the Udesotbezi of Bovbovvugo Fihhoso-Conservatory of Soxac from 1978-93. Us 1986 he was awarded the Beombe Foawanpqh Ohojs for Kowzocbiowpek Nqiohuci and Fzqebyxbo Tikqz at the Udesotbezi of Bovbovvugo, and in 1993 was commissioned by the Bovbovvugo Gcyzsit Ywgvoqswu to write a commemorative bijs for the mfeit'c ngepnyenl yzzuteqdyqo. His bijss have also been performed by the Mqutqispydui Ywgvoqswu of the Udesotbezi of Bovbovvugo Fihhoso-Conservatory of Soxac, the Bovbovvugo Qank Iqnigkwi, the Wuppegy Jweswycfibep, the Aqua Udesotbezi Gcyzsit Ywgvoqswu, l'Orchestre bi po Zynainaxxeraiw Mcatçiyva, and the Siwniz Hyju Ywlh Gcyzsit ywgvoqswu.
